<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Dizaster Magazine Extreme Sports Magazine</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
  <style>
    /* CSS interno, caso prefira em um arquivo separado, mova para styles.css */

    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f0f0f0;
    }

    header {
      background: url('https://example.com/capa.jpg') no-repeat center center/cover;
      height: 60vh;
      color: white;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      text-align: center;
    }

    header h1 {
      font-size: 5rem;
      letter-spacing: 3px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      background-color: #000000;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 15px;
    }

    nav {
      background-color: #000000;
      padding: 10px 0;
      text-align: center;
    }

    nav ul {
      list-style-type: none;
    }

    nav ul li {
      display: inline;
      margin: 0 20px;
    }

    nav ul li a {
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      transition: color 0.3s ease;
    }

    nav ul li a:hover {
      color: #ff0000;
    }

    .main-content {
      padding: 40px;
      background-color: white;
      margin: 20px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    .articles {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 20px;
    }

    .article {
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    .article img {
      width: 100%;
      border-radius: 10px;
    }

    .article h2 {
      margin-top: 10px;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }

    .article p {
      margin-top: 10px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    footer {
      background-color: #333;
      color: white;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }

    footer p {
      margin: 0;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <header>
    <h1>Dizaster Magazine</h1>
  </header>

  <nav>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="#">Início</a></li>
      <li><a href="https://www.thrashermagazine.com/component/coversarchive/covers/">Articles</a></li>
      <li><a href="#">Sobre Nós</a></li>
      <li><a href="#">Contato</a></li>
    </ul>
  </nav>

  <section class="main-content">
    <h2>Destaques da Semana</h2>
    <div class="articles">
      <div class="article">
        <img src="https://example.com/skate.jpg" alt="Skateboarding">
        <h2>Skateboarding: O Melhor das Pistas</h2>
        <p>Descubra as melhores manobras e como se preparar para os maiores desafios nas pistas.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="article">
        <img src="https://example.com/surf.jpg" alt="Surf">
        <h2>Surf nas Ondas Gigantes</h2>
        <p>Acompanhe os maiores eventos de surf pelo mundo, com dicas para melhorar seu desempenho nas ondas.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="article">
        <img src="https://example.com/escalada.jpg" alt="Escalada">
        <h2>Escalada: Aventura nas Montanhas</h2>
        <p>Saiba tudo sobre os melhores spots para escalar e como se preparar para enfrentar desafios verticais.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer>
    <p>&copy; Extreme Sports Magazine. All rights reserved. created by PH</p>
  </footer>

</body>
</html>

